  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC286">
        <l>iṟṟuniṉ ṟicaikku mēye ṉiṟuti</l>
        <l>kūṟṟuvayi ṉōraḷa pākalu murittē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/173/mode/1up">173</ref>.</p>
      <p>
urai: mēṟ collappaṭṭa aintu ēkārattuḷḷum īṟṟacai ēkāram ōraḷapām eṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC286-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘kaṭalpōṟ ṟōṉṟala kāṭiṟan tōrē'</l>
        <trailer>[akam - 1]</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <p>
ummai etirmaṟaiyākaliṉ kuṟaiyātu niṟṟalē perumpāṉmai. (38)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n224/mode/1up">221</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ. ceyyuḷiṟutikkaṇ niṉṟicaikkum īṟṟacaiyēkāraṅ kūṟṟiṭattu orumāttiraittākalumurittu. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u - m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC286-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘kaṭalpōṟ ṟōṉṟala kāṭiṟan tōrē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpuḻi ōraḷapāyiṉavāṟu kaṇṭukoḷka.
      </p>
      <p>
tēṟṟamutalāyiṉa nīkki īṟṟacaiyē taḻuvutaṟku īṟṟuniṉṟicaikkumeṉṟār. ceyyuḷiṭai niṟpataṉai nīkkutaṟku īṟṟuniṉṟicaikkumeṉṟēyoḻiyātu iṟutiyeṉṟār. mēṉiṉṟa ceyyuḷuṟuppoṭu poruntak kūṟutaṟkaṇeṉpār kūṟṟuvayiṉeṉṟār.
      </p>
      <p>
ummai etirmaṟai.	(38)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/310/mode/1up">310</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/311/mode/1up">311</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/312/mode/1up">312</ref>.</p>
      <p>
      īṟṟacai yēkārattiṟ kaḷapoṉṟu
      </p>
      <lg>
        <l>iṟṟu niṉ ṟicaikku mēye ṉiṟuti</l>
        <l>kūṟṟuvayi ṉōraḷa pākalu murittē.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
iḵtu, īṟṟacai yēkārattiṟku vēṟō rilakkaṇaṅ kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) īṟṟuniṉṟicaikku mēyeṉiṟuti ― ceyyuḷiṟutikkaṇiṉ ṟicaikku mīṟṟacaiyēkāram, kūṟṟuvayiṉ ― ac ceyyuḷiṭattup pāveṉṉu muṟuppiṉai nilaipeṟak kūṟumiṭattu, ōraḷapākalu murittē ― taṉakkuriya viraṇṭu māttiraiyē yaṉṟip piṉṉarumoru māttirai yuṇṭāy varutalu muritteṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
ummaiyāṉ mūṉṟu māttirai peṟā tiraṇṭu māttirai peṟṟuvarutalu murittāyiṟṟu. pāveṉṉu muṟuppiṉai nilaipeṟak kūṟumiṭattu mūṉṟu māttirai peṟuvatu ceyyuḷiṟutikka ṇiṟkum īṟṟacaiyē yeṉpataṟivittaṟku ē yeṉiṟuti yeṉṟu mīṭṭuṅ kūṟiṉār.
      </p>
      <p>
(u-m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC286-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘kaṭalpō ṟōṉṟala kāṭiṟan tōrēe’</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC286-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘akilpaṭu kaḷḷiyaṅ kāṭiṟan tōrēe’</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC286-Nacc-cit3">
       <l>‘taṇkaṭal vēliniṉ kuṭanā ṭaṟṟēe’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
ivai pōlvaṉa piṟacāṉṟōr ceyyuṭ kaḷellām mūṉṟu māttirai peṟṟup pāveṉṉu muṟuppai viḷakki niṟkumāṟu kāṇka.
      </p>
      <p>
iṉi,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC286-Nacc-cit4">
       <l>‘avarēee kēṭil viḻupporuṭarumār pācilai</l>
       <l>vāṭā vaḷḷiyaṅ kāṭiṟan tōrēe’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉac ceyyuḷiṭaikkaṇ varumīṟṟacai yēkāra miraṇṭu māttirai peṟṟup pāveṉṉu muṟuppai viḷakki niṉṟavāṟu  kāṇka. iḵtīṟṟacai yākaliṟ ceyyuḷiyaliṟ kūṟu māttirai yeṉṉu muṟuppiṉkaṇ aṭaṅkāteṉ ṟīṇṭuk kūṟiṉār. atu perumpāṉmai poruṭaruñ coṟkē vitiyākaliṉ. <num xml:lang="en">(38)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n189/mode/1up">182</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n190/mode/1up">183</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ēkārattiṟku uriyatōr marapu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
        i-ḷ: ― ceyyuḷ iṟutikkaṇ niṉṟu olikkum ēkāram collumiṭattu orumāttiraiyāki niṟkavum peṟum. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
        u-m:―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC286-Tey-cit1">
        <l>kaṭalpōṟ <app><lem wit="#Ed">ṟōṉṟala</lem><rdg wit="#pāṭapētam">ṟōṉṟal</rdg></app> kāṭiṟan tōrē.</l>
        <trailer>(akam ― 1)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
itu oru māttiraiyāki niṟkum.	[37]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
